  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nCI does not check for failing builds.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nCI should fail early if `yarn build` returns an error.\r\n\r\n**Steps to Reproduce**\r\n\r\nThe following PRs have all-green CI tests even though they do not build properly.\r\n* #3166\r\n* #3163\r\n* #3158\r\n* #3148\r\n* #3144\r\n* #3141\r\n\r\nWe might be caching dependencies too aggressively?",
