    "body": "Yes, I can reproduce this locally:\r\n\r\n`yarn clean && lerna run build` succeeds.\r\n\r\nBut:\r\n\r\n`yarn install && yarn clean && lerna run build` fails.\r\n\r\nWe are caching dependencies and do not reinstall unless we change the ~~NodeJS version~~ yarn lock file.",
